			ROX-Filer
			A RISCOS-like filer for X
			by Thomas Leonard

			Using

It's pretty similar to the RISC OS filer. Right-click for a menu of choices.

Press Backspace to change to the parent directory in the same window.

Drag things to copy them.
Shift+Drag things to move them.
Shift+Ctrl+Drag things to create symlinks.

